						<span class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50 text-slate-300 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-sm">3</span>
						<div>
							<p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed"><span class="font-medium text-slate-200">Descargar:</span> Descarga el componente como archivo .tsx listo para usar.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/20 border border-slate-800/30 hover:border-slate-700/50 transition-all duration-500">
						<span class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50 text-slate-300 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-sm">4</span>
